%% Trace: features/04-補綁Email.feature + 05-補綁手機發送OTP + 06-補綁手機完成綁定.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Ctrl as AccountBindingController
    participant Auth as JwtAuthGuard
    participant Svc as SupplementaryBindingService
    participant OtpSvc as OtpService
    participant SMS as ItSmsGateway
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant CRM as CrmCustomerGateway

    Note over User,FE: 使用者已登入 (Bearer token)

    alt 補綁 Email (不需 OTP, BR-14)
        User->>FE: 帳號設定 → 綁定 Email → 輸入 Email
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /account/bindings/email (email) [Bearer]
        Ctrl->>Auth: validateJwt
        Auth-->>Ctrl: currentUserId
        Ctrl->>Svc: bindEmail(memberAuthId=currentUserId, email)
        Svc->>Repo: findByEmailHash(emailHash) - 確認唯一性
        Repo-->>Svc: null (free)
        Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET email, email_hash WHERE id
        Svc->>CRM: updateCustomerEmail(customer_id, email)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: bound
        Ctrl-->>FE: 201 Created
    else 補綁手機 (兩步)
        %% Step 1: send OTP with uniqueness pre-check
        User->>FE: 帳號設定 → 綁定手機 → 輸入手機
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /account/bindings/mobile/send-otp (mobile) [Bearer]
        Ctrl->>Auth: validateJwt
        Ctrl->>Svc: prepareMobileBind(currentUserId, mobile)
        Svc->>Repo: findByMobileHash - 唯一性
        Repo-->>Svc: null (free)
        Svc->>OtpSvc: issue(contact=mobile, purpose=REGISTER, channel=sms)
        OtpSvc->>SMS: enqueue
        OtpSvc-->>Svc: otp_uuid
        Svc-->>Ctrl: otp_uuid
        Ctrl-->>FE: 200 {otp_uuid}

        %% Step 2: verify OTP + write contact
        User->>FE: 輸入 OTP
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /account/bindings/mobile (otp_uuid, otp_code) [Bearer]
        Ctrl->>Svc: bindMobile(currentUserId, otp_uuid, otp_code)
        Svc->>OtpSvc: verify(otp_uuid, otp_code)
        OtpSvc-->>Svc: ok (contact_hash)
        Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET mobile_phone, mobile_phone_hash
        Svc->>CRM: updateCustomerMobile(customer_id, mobile)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: bound
        Ctrl-->>FE: 201 Created
    end
    FE-->>User: 完成，兩種方式皆可登入
